Another one—but this isn’t just any new spot. This time, we’re right in the heart of Gurgaon’s most happening hub!
Welcome to one8 Commune Golf Course Road—a space that’s warm & inviting, a brand-new menu, and an experience that feels fresh yet unmistakably Commune.
We’ve built something special here, and we can’t wait for you to be a part of it. See you soon, Gurgaon!

Noida is officially #Kohlified!

We’re opening our doors tonight, and we can’t wait to welcome you!

With an incredible menu featuring classic favorites and exclusive signature cocktails, we’ve got something for every Noida taste bud. Add to that an ambience that’s just right, and you’ve got the perfect spot to unwind.

When will we see you?

Book your experience now!
